------------------------------------
de_trash_metall_s - originally by BUZZER, re-made by Dv8 
------------------------------------

T`s win by planting and exploding the bomb or eliminating the CT`s
CT`s win by stopping the T`s from exploding the bomb or eliminating the T`s.

This map is originally from CS 1.6 and made by Buzzer. Any and All credit to Buzzer. I re-made this for CS Source as a lot of players on our 1.6 custom map server enjoyed it.
It is a rather small very fast paced 24 player bomb map bordering on a dm type atmosphere. Both bomb sites are a stones throw from each other.
